```
ANALYZE THUMBNAIL IMAGE:
Channel Size: [subscriber count]
Niche: [Gaming|Education|Entertainment|Tech|Review|Finance|Vlog]

EVALUATE:
1. Visual Contrast (0-10): [Score]
