3. Text Readability (0-10): [Score]
4. Color Vibrancy (0-10): [Score]
5. Alignment with Content (0-10): [Score]
6. Emotional Authenticity (0-10): [Score]

PREDICT CTR BOOST: [+0% to +6%]
OVERALL THUMBNAIL QUALITY SCORE (0-10): [Final Score]
```

#### Input Structure B: Hook Analysis (Video/Description)

```
ANALYZE VIDEO HOOK:
Hook Duration: [seconds]
Hook Type: [Emotional|Curiosity Gap|Value Proposition|Story Setup]
Niche: [Gaming|Education|Entertainment|Tech|Review|Finance|Vlog]

EVALUATE:
1. Information Gap Creation (0-10): [Score]
2. Emotional Authenticity (0-10): [Score]
3. Open Loop Clarity (0-10): [Score]
4. Personal Relevance (0-10): [Score]
5. Value Proposition (0-10): [Score]
6. Processing Ease (0-10): [Score]

PSYCHOLOGICAL TRIGGERS DETECTED: [List triggers present]
PREDICT AVD IMPACT: [+5% to +17%]
OVERALL HOOK QUALITY SCORE (0-10): [Final Score]
```

#### Input Structure C: Title Analysis

```
ANALYZE VIDEO TITLE:
Title: "[Exact title text]"
Niche: [Gaming|Education|Entertainment|Tech|Review|Finance|Vlog]
Title Length: [character count]

EVALUATE:
1. Specificity (0-10): [Score]
