CALCULATE:
Channel Size Category: [Nano|Micro|Small|Large|Mega]
Channel Size Multiplier: [0.5 to 4.0]
Channel Authority Factor: [0.6 to 1.2]
Consistency Bonus: [0.8 to 1.2]
```

